Copyright (c) 2022 HeartMail Inc.

OpenSPV is the reference implementation of all of the protocols of the Social
Bitcoin Web (SBW).

Every commit to OpenSPV is open to consortium members but closed to outsiders.

For every commit to OpenSPV, the commit changes to the OpenBSV license one year
after the commit was made.

Consortium members are added and removed at the sole discretion of HeartMail
Inc. Any consortium member who is removed retains the license for the software
up through the latest commit before they were removed.

