Thus, there are two periods for every commit:

- The closed period.
- The open period.

During the closed period:

- Consortium members are free to sell or license proprietary software that
  bundles OpenSPV inside as a dependency.
- Consortium members are not free to sell or license OpenSPV as an isolated
  package.

During open period, the license changes to OpenBSV. The text of the OpenBSV
license follows:

